0xF08E42BFA46BDFF8.name: _GET_WAYPOINT_POSITION
0xF08E42BFA46BDFF8.comment: Unlike `GET_WAYPOINT_COORDS - 0x29B30D07C3F7873B`, which returns a single value, this native returns the x and y coordinates of the waypoint separately as floats from pointer. To retrieve each coordinate, `Citizen.PointerValueFloat()` must be used with this function.
